lyrics.stanza:
I will not be afraid;
I will not be afraid;
  I will look upward,
  And travel onward,
    And not be afraid.

He says He will be with me;
He says He will be with me;
  He goes before me,
  And is beside me,
    So I'm not afraid.

His arms are underneath me;
His arms are underneath me;
  His hand upholds me,
  His love enfolds me,
    So I'm not afraid.

His Word will stand for ever;
His Word will stand for ever;
  His truth it shall be
  My shield and buckler,
    So I'm not afraid.

He will give grace and glory;
He will give grace and glory;
  His cross before me,
  His banner o'er me,
    So I'm not afraid.

So we go singing onward;
So we go singing onward;
  We're pressing forward,
  We're marching upward,
    To Him unafraid.
